Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you calm your emotions and\Nplay normally, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play with stirred emotions, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I calmed down with those 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,While you probably became upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:57.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,He's completely been overwhelmed.\NThere's no way he can win like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I win by four and a half moku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.11,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(360,115)}The Thirty-Second Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:08.11,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}The Last day of the Preliminaries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:12.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs19\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\frz345\pos(378,166)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:12.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(667,0)\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,362)}Second day of the Pro Exam Preliminaries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.91,Background,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Hikaru... you're still not relaxed today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:01.78,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}If you lose the control of your mind, the thought\Nbehind each of your moves begin to break apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Now that I think about it, you were like this during the Insei examination too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}You couldn't play the way you usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:15.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}And your moves become rushed, you went in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.63,Background,,0,0,0,,so please halt your clocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.36,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat lunch! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought lunch this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What for!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to finish it, Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, Shindou isn't doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:03.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If he loses today, he'll be at the\Nend of the rope with two losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Mind my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.43,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, umm, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm trying to think right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do!? I got my second win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Looks like you got your second\Nloss. You're at the end of your rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:52.44,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(667,667)\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,362)}Third day of the pro exam preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.16,Background,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's almost time for the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.52,Sai,,0,0,0,,You already have two losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in as late as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that I don't meet Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to get a win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.45,Background,,0,0,0,,My opponent today is Fuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.39,Background,,0,0,0,,I've only lost to Fuku twice out of\Nall the games we played for fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.60,Background,,0,0,0,,and all the games during the study sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.97,Background,,0,0,0,,I should be able to beat Fuku if I play normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.37,Background,,0,0,0,,Fuku is probably desperate being one and one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I play normally I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:45.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Play normally... that becomes harder\Nthe more desperate you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun! What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter, go sit down already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You came in at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The clock's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Don't let your feelings take control, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like speaking to someone who's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But, didn't he say something earlier about giving\Nhim money so that he can take the pro exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inseis take it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked to take a day off of school awhile ago too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he told his teacher already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.88,Background,,0,0,0,,I thought he was too into it back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd ask you dad, about\Nwhat it's like to be a pro player.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know anything either,\Nthough I do like Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Masao say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "It's hard to become a pro no\Nmatter who it is. He'll probably drop the\Nexam. Let him do what he wants."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with him. Just let Hikaru\Ndo what he wants for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:57.20,Background,,0,0,0,,It feels like Hikaru's changing... I feel uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Hikaru want to become\Na pro all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost to a boy his age by a lot\Nat Go, and he was given up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:20.31,Memory,,0,0,0,,He looked disappointed, and became pro.\NSo I want to make him look back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:37.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The eyes he had when he first came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:42.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll make him turn those eyes to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}How fortunate that the opponent is\Nsomeone you're used to playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}You're back to your normal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for lunch, so please halt your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You're already in the end game?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to play to the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:28.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was worried for Shindou-kun because he got two\Nstraight losses, but he's playing the way he usually does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.25,Background,,0,0,0,,I have 50 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.30,Background,,0,0,0,,I have 59 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! One win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One win!? Shindou-kun you lost twice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you didn't know? I would've been out if I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:10:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I won. Oh yeah... now Fuku\Nyou're one and two just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm going to go home. I don't want\Nto bump into that hairy godzilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you came at the\Nlast minute this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to come at the\Nlast minute tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have drawings again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.49,Background,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:29.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It makes sense for the winner to record the game.\NI'd hate to mark down my own losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:36.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Fukui... Fukui... and then my win...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three and a half moku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll grab a win again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:02.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Tomorrow... you have two losses still\Ntomorrow. That won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinryuji-san lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to tell me that you're a pro right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm an Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing at a Go Salon like this\Noccasionally is good practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:49.84,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, an Insei, here to practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a friend who's a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,According to him, if the age limit for the\Nexam wasn't 30, I could take it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're strong enough!" He told me, but\Nseems like he was just being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I didn't put up much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.71,Background,,0,0,0,,Over here mister, you played here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had kosumi'd here, I would\Nhave been in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, are you done? Want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Try going to this Go Salon. You want\Nto play good people right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing at a Go salon is fun but the smoke is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play at my house, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Isumi-san, let's stop by the Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To see the pro exam preliminaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.12,Background,,0,0,0,,Today's the third day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.25,Background,,0,0,0,,Let's go see if Shindou's risen\Nup with three straight wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:08.27,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs42.5\bord1\1c&H679299&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\frz10\pos(320,31)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:08.27,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(751,0)\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,362)}Pro Exam Preliminaries Day 4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.12,Background,,0,0,0,,What!? Waya and Isumi-san dropped\Nby afterwards yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. In the afternoon, to check the match records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told them that Fuku and Shindou\Nfinished in the morning and went home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya said "Those two always play so quickly."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We used a lot of time that game for Fuku and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The people with three wins\Nand three losses are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And all that's left are people who are 1-2 and 2-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya said "Shindou that idiot, what is he doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just you Shindou, I have two losses,\NFuku has two losses... it's really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To think, Iijima-kun got three wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Where's Tsubaki!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The beard guy got three wins and moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll begin the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come forward to draw a number\Nwhen your name is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:24.10,Background,,0,0,0,,If you've already played your opponent,\Nplease say so, we'll redo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}If two people with two losses play\Neach other, one of them will fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:46.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}That move he played now, it seems\Nlike a good move, but it's a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:49.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}If Hikaru responds correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}It ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:16.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,Like I said! If you had only played\Nlike that on the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:20.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,But noooo you were afraid of the bearded\Nguy and you lost. I'm so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Fuku won too. Now Fuku and I are both 2-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:28.27,Background,,0,0,0,,Will you mark me down too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. By resignation. I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nase is 2-2 too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We might play each other tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be less people too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.83,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll go watch the other games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's finally the last day of the preliminaries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll take... a win tomorrow too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:07.24,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\bord1\1c&H3C5F80&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(487,194)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:07.24,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(417,0)\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,362)}Pro Exam Preliminaries Day 5
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Two boards... this decides everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.14,Background,,0,0,0,,Looks like everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:37.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There are five people with 2-2. Two of us will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:41.43,Background,,0,0,0,,We'll begin drawing for the pairings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku and Shindou-kun have played\Neach other on the third day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone else played someone here? No right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if Fuku-kun is playing\NShindou-kun, we'll redo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Everyone please come forward and draw a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm B.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm B too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hirabayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Hirabayashi and Fuku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm A.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm A.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nase-kun and Matsui-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun you don't have an opponent\Nand you win by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Win by... default...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.16,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs42.5\bord1\1c&H587893&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(368,42)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,YAHOO! I won without playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.58,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite! You're unlucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:43.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you need to play as\Nmany games as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.48,Background,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,You're going to play that bearded guy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a month till the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll train! I'll train!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.08,Sai,,0,0,0,,Train? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I'll think about it when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.21,Sai,,0,0,0,,Think about it now! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh you're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Morishita 9 dan's Study\NSession is this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go home only to come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play on a magnet Go board to kill time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,~Wai~ I'll play! I'll play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou and the other guys with two losses... if\Nthey won yesterday, they should still be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they have three losses, they would've failed\Nyesterday, and they wouldn't be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If he failed... Shindou might not come\Nto the study session today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:56.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Fuku and Nase and the outsiders are the\Nonly ones playing. Did Shindou fail!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.83,Background,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hairy Godzilla!? You lost because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was by default, you made\Nit to the exam, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, I thought you'd come\Nup with three straight wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd get defeated by a hairy godzilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I just kind of got angry and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! You'd come with us, the next time\NIsumi-san and I go to a Go Salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Salon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to play against people\Nlike that hairy godzilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.66,Background,,0,0,0,,You've got to get used to it by the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be done by now. Let's go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:50.73,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey mom? It's me. Yeah, it just ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.00,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:58.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! All three of you made it to the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.61,Background,,0,0,0,,Man, you really had me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares! We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? Just\Nyesterday you were going,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"where's the hairy godzilla? Where's\Nthe hairy godzilla?" in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:38.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFEFECE&}Oh well, I'm just glad you won.
