Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue with Tesuji today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's white's turn. Right now, these three\Nwhite stones are about to get captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But there's a way to save them\Nby taking these black stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:23.83,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\1c&H167AF3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(314,330)}How would you save the white stones
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:23.83,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\1c&H167AF3&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(314,430)}by capturing the black stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.46,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fad(209,209)\1c&HF80001&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(240,354)}Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:32.18,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fad(209,209)\1c&HFF20F9&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(520,242)}Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay last move, do it with energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:34.40,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fad(209,209)\1c&HF50004&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(316,336)}Yuuki is correct!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, you can take these black stones like this.
