Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.78,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fad(209,0)\1c&H341FEB&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(507,342)}"A Nesting Swan"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this time?
