Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:46.34,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,These feelings I want to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.00,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,are spilling out right now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:21:02.70,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,but I'm hesitating, not knowing how to put it into words
