Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.28,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,Let's start each of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:43.20,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,our departure here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:48.70,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,I'm not like I was before
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:54.00,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,I won't give up anymore, I'll keep on walking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:58.70,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,no matter what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.70,Ed3English,,0,0,0,,So that I can become stronger.
